posting_body: ['RELAXATION & CHARM', 'Located less than 15 minutes from downtown Olympia, WA, Woodbury Apartments boasts a convenient Lacey location near shopping and dining options while keeping you close to the city.', 'At Woodbury, expansive green spaces create the perfect backdrop for amenities that include a sparkling pool, fenced dog park and even a basketball court and playground.', 'Discover everything awaiting you.', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 18', 'OR Text', '18', 'to', 'show contact info', 'for more information.', 'Need more information?', 'Copy this link:', '<URL>', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath, approximately 967 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Features', '- Wood-Style Flooring', '- Vaulted Ceilings*', '- Electric Fireplaces', '- Storage', '- Washer & Dryer', '- Private Patio/Balcony', '- Stainless Steel Appliances', '- Pantry', '- Walk-In Closets', '- LED Lighting', '*In select units.', 'Community Amenities', '- Playground', '- Resort-Style Pool', '- 24-Hr Pet Wash', '- Basketball Court', '- Secured 24-Hr Pkg Locker Room', '- State of the Art Fitness Center', '- Green Initiative', '- Off-Leash Pet Park', '- Gated Electronic Entrance', '- Resort-Style Spa', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats and dogs allowed.', 'We welcome 2 pets per apartment home.', 'There is a $250 pet deposit for 1 pet and $375 for 2 pets and a $250 non-refundable pet fee for 1 pet and $375 for 2 pets.', 'Pet rent is $30 per month per pet.', 'No weight limit, but some breed restrictions apply.', 'Please call our leasing office for complete Pet Policy.', 'Office Hours', 'Mon - Fri: By appointment only', 'Sat: Closed', 'Sun: Closed', 'Woodbury', '3425 Polo Club Lane SE, Olympia, WA, 98501', 'We do not accept Comprehensive Reusable Tenant Screening Reports as defined by and pursuant to RCW 59.18.', 'uTlF38rb']
